===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Pictogram of a square-shaped bamboo basket (perhaps originally made to contain millet and rice); the inner component is [[㞷]], which today retains only the bottom component [[王]] as a phonetic element. The inner component The original form is [[匩]] and the original meaning is preserved in [[筐]].

